  "text": "Observing that (3.7) is continuous, we know that (3.7) has at most one crossing limit cycle by [CITATION_1] Corollary 3] again. Finally, we conclude that (3.1) has at most one crossing limit cycle because (3.6) is a homeomorphism.",
